<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Albrecht von Wertheim, Bischof von Bamberg</head><p>Der Rat kündigt den Samuel N., Jude zu Nürnberg, wegen des Streits mit Erhard Stieber bei dem vor dem Veitstag in Bamberg angesetzten Gerichtstag an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_132" id="65v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_132_r3l1">Bẏſſchof cʒu <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_132_r3l2"><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / Als vns ewr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> vvider <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat von Erhart </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_132_r3l3">Stẏebers vnd Sanvvals <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> Juden vvegen / vnd <expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_132_r3l4">Juden <expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan> rechtage auf den Dornſtag vor ſant veits tag ſchierſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_132_r3l5">für <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade gen <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> beſcheiden hat / Alſo maint derſelb ~ Jude </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_132_r3l6">
<del rend="strikethrough">yn </del> darümb für <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade <expan>cʒekume<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> cʒeſuchen / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_132_r3l7">daʒ Jr <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Juden cʒum rehten <expan>beuolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſein laſſen vvöllet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_132_r3l8">durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vville<ex>n</ex></expan> / Alſo daʒ Jm des <expan>ſlewnigklıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> geholffen vverde Als </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_132_r3l9">etc / das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_132" id="65v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Bysschof czu <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns ewr
                            <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> wider
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat von Erhart Styebers
                        und Sanwals, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> juden, wegen und
                                <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> juden <expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan> rechtage
                        <app><note><q type="date">auf den dornstag vor sant Veits tag schierst</q>12.06.1410</note></app> für <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
                        gnade gen <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> bescheiden hat. Also maint derselb
                        jude darümb für <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade <expan>cze
                            kume<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> cze suchen.
                                <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
                        gnaden <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> juden czum rehten
                                <expan>bevolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein lassen wöllet durch
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>, also daz im des
                                <expan>slewnigklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> geholffen werde, als etc. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
